Body: It's true that current cryptocurrencies struggle with scalability, fees and transaction times. The networks are usually overloaded or they become too expensive for micropayments. Therefore, a neat solution would be quite interesting. The idea of hubs combined with off-chain transactions is actually very interesting and may be at least temporary solution and improvement. The project is well designed so it's quite promising.
